#
# This file contain three groups of target rules:
#
# 1.  FPtools targets
#	depend*
#	runtests*
#
# 2.  GNU standard targets
#	all*
#	install* uninstall installcheck installdirs
#	clean* distclean* mostlyclean* maintainer-clean*
